Security best practices
-----------------------

**Least privilege Bindle configuration**:

.. code-block:: json

   {
     "bindleConfiguration": {
       "pipeline": "my-service-pipeline",
       "permissions": [
         {
           "action": "pipelines:UpdatePipeline",
           "resource": "arn:aws:pipelines:*:*:pipeline/my-service-pipeline",
           "conditions": {
             "StringEquals": {
               "pipelines:SourcePackage": "MyServiceCDK"
             }
           }
         },
         {
           "action": "pipelines:CreateStage",
           "resource": "arn:aws:pipelines:*:*:pipeline/my-service-pipeline/stage/*",
           "conditions": {
             "StringLike": {
               "pipelines:StageName": ["Beta-*", "Gamma-*", "Prod-*"]
             }
           }
         },
         {
           "action": "pipelines:ModifyApprovalWorkflow",
           "resource": "arn:aws:pipelines:*:*:pipeline/my-service-pipeline/workflow/*",
           "conditions": {
