Advanced troubleshooting scenarios
----------------------------------

**Scenario 1: Cross-account pipeline updates failing**

.. code-block:: bash

   # Diagnose cross-account permission issues
   #!/bin/bash

   SOURCE_ACCOUNT="111111111111"
   TARGET_ACCOUNT="222222222222"
   PIPELINE="cross-account-pipeline"

   # Check role assumptions
   aws sts assume-role \
     --role-arn "arn:aws:iam::${TARGET_ACCOUNT}:role/PipelineUpdateRole" \
     --role-session-name "test-session" \
     --query 'Credentials.SessionToken' \
     --output text

